se.lnu.advsd.meysam.ActivityCalendarApi

Interface ActivityCalendarApi

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivityCalendarApiImpl

    public interface ActivityCalendarApi
    Makes it possible to define activities with predefined budgets for events in google calendar and add new events with some a specified time bidget.
    Author:
    Meysam M. Fard
